# NAME: Disney
# AUTHOR: steak
# TYPE: Quantumult X Filter
# DESCRIPTION: Disney+ 日常分流规则，适合手机 / iPad / 网页轻量使用
# SOURCE: Based on blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script Disney rules
# UPDATED: 2026-05-11
#
# ================================
# 使用说明
# ================================
# 1. 文件名建议：Disney.list
# 2. 适用于：Quantumult X [filter_remote]
# 3. 策略组名称：Disney+
# 4. 这是日常精简版，主要覆盖 Disney+ App / 网页 / 播放 / 登录 / CDN
# 5. 如果 QX 对策略组名里的 + 号兼容不好，可把策略组改名为 DisneyPlus，并同步替换规则里的 Disney+
#
# QX 远程订阅示例：
# https://raw.githubusercontent.com/你的用户名/你的仓库/main/Rules/Disney.list, tag=Disney, force-policy=Disney+, update-interval=86400, opt-parser=false, enabled=true
#
# ================================
# Disney+ 核心服务
# ================================

HOST,cdn.registerdisney.go.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,disneyplus.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,disney-plus.net,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,dssott.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,dssedge.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,bamgrid.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,disneystreaming.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,streamingdisney.net,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,disneysubscription.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,disneyplus.bn5x.net,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,disneyplus.com.ssl.sc.omtrdc.net,Disney+

# ================================
# Disney+ API / 账号 / 设备 / 播放相关
# ================================

HOST-SUFFIX,dmed.technology,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,dtci.co,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,dtci.technology,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,edgedatg.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,go.com,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com,Disney+

# ================================
# Disney+ 统计 / 风控 / 体验监控
# ================================

HOST-SUFFIX,disney.demdex.net,Disney+
HOST-SUFFIX,disney.my.sentry.io,Disney+
